item.description:
Hi Folks,

We're going to the Black and White Rocks in the Middlesex Fells for some climbing tomorrow at 11 AM. Meet in the parking lot at East Border Road near Woodland Road. If you miss us, you can find us at Crag 1--Pinnacle Rock. It's a few hundred feet up and to the right along the path that starts near the intersection of the roads.

All are welcomed. Â Bring rope, long slings for anchors, harness, shoes, etc.

For more information, see:

http://www.rockclimbing.com/routes/North_America/United_States/Massachusetts/Greater_Boston/Black_and_White_Rocks/

http://www.mass.gov/dcr/parks/metroboston/fells.htm

Ken
item.name: Black and White Rocks in the Fells
